<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Bootstrap Example</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<h1>Welcome to the Msg API</h1>
<img src='https://media.giphy.com/media/JltOMwYmi0VrO/giphy.gif'>

<h3>🤓 Check out these endpoints! 💾</h3>
</center>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <center><h3>🧓 Users</h3></center>
        <ul>
          <li>Users index: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/users'>/users</a></li>
          <li>Users show: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/users/1'>/users/:id</a></li>
          <li>See a Users messages: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/users/1/messages'>/users/:id/messages</a></li>
          <li>See a Users conversations: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/users/1/conversations'>/users/:id/conversations</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <center><h3>💬 Messages</h3></center>
        <ul>
          <li>Messages index: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/messages'>/messages</a></li>
          <li>Too much info for ya? Limit it to a few messages: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/messages?number_messages=10'>/messages?limit_messages=10</a></li>
          <li>Or limit by date range: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/messages?days_ago=1'>/messages?days_ago=1</a></li>
          <li>See <a href="https://github.com/TheLucasMoore/msg#posting-messages">the docs</a> for posting new messages.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <center><h3>📥 Conversations</h3></center>
        <ul>
          <li>See the users in a conversation: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/conversations/1/users'>conversations/:id/users</a></li>
          <li>See messages in a conversation: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/conversations/1'>/conversations/:id</a></li>
          <li>You can also limit this by number of messages: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/conversations/1?number_messages=10'>/conversations/1?number_messages=10</a></li>
          <li>You can also also limit this by a date range: <a href='https://msg-api-3000.herokuapp.com/conversations/1?days_ago=1'>/conversations/1?days_ago=1</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<center>
<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
<p>I don't call myself a front end developer, this template is from <a href='https://www.w3schools.com/bootstrap/bootstrap_grid_large.asp' target='_blank'>here</a>. 😎</p>
</center>
</body>
</html>